text: Gerald Quentin Maguire Jr from the KTH Royal Institute of Technology in Kista, Stockholm, Sweden was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for contributions to mobile networks and cognitive radio systems. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:KTH Royal Institute of Technology faculty Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
